  "original_title": "\u0dbd\u0d82\u0d9a\u0dcf\u0db4\u0dd4\u0dbb \u0db4\u0dbb\u0dd2\u0db4\u0dcf\u0dbd\u0db1 \u0db1\u0dd2\u0dbd\u0db0\u0dcf\u0dbb\u0dd2\u0db1\u0dd2\u0dba \u0d9d\u0dcf\u0dad\u0db1\u0dba\u0da7 \u0dc3\u0dd0\u0db8\u0dd2\u0dba\u0dcf \u0d85\u0dad\u0dca\u0d85\u0da9\u0d82\u0d9c\u0dd4\u0dc0\u0da7",
  "text_idx": {
    "en": {
      "title": "Husband arrested for murdering Lankapura administrative officer",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "The Lankapura police say that her husband was arrested on suspicion of murdering the chief administrative officers of the Lankapura Divisional Secretariat along with the ax allegedly used in the killing on the evening of (5).",
        "On the 4th at around 2:30 in the morning, Ms. Yamuna Padmini, an administrative officer, was killed while she was residing at her house in Talpotha Lankapura. Herat Mudiansela's husband, Kapila Senarath Bandara (41), the father of two children, was arrested on suspicion of this. .P. K. Mr. Pathirana said.",
        "According to the investigating police, the suspect confessed to the police that his wife scolded him not to come home after drinking alcohol, and to pay the debt due, and as a result of an argument between the two, he attacked him with an axe.",
        "Statements of another suspect related to this murder will be obtained and further investigation of the incident will be conducted by Polonnaruwa Senior Superintendent of Police Mr. Oshan Hewawitharana. P. K. A team of police officers including Mr. Pathirana."
      ],
